description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Guided Run | BEGINNER FRIENDLY' from the channel Taylor Christine Hall.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Mindful Walk vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Here is a beginner friendly 20 minute follow along run that you can do outside or on a tread! Plug your headphones in a listen to me guide you through this 20 minute workout that will leave your body and mind feeling rejuvenated and refreshed! This is a beginner friendly run that you can do outside or on a tread! Let's get after it for the next 20 minutes, and don't forget to warm up before you begin running!!

you can take my 5 minute pre-run warmup here: 
https://youtu.be/VocwVwb_sMI

WELCOME BACK WARRIORS!!
Welcome back to my channel, or if this is your first time here, welcome to my channel! I am SO excited to announce my new 'Train With Tay' series!! I will be posting guided runs and follow-along core workouts each week so that you guys can throw some headphones on and workout anywhere at anytime!! Let me know how you guys are feeling after this run!
